#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.115"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.115:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.115:0.2"
msgid "12. Āpāyikavagga "
msgstr "12. Bound for Loss "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.115:0.3"
msgid "115. Appameyyasutta "
msgstr "115. Immeasurable "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.115:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these three people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.115:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.115:1.3"
msgid "Suppameyyo, duppameyyo, appameyyo. "
msgstr "Someone easy to measure, someone hard to measure, and someone who is immeasurable. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.115:1.4"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo suppameyyo? "
msgstr "And who is the person easy to measure? "

msgctxt "an3.115:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo uddhato hoti unnaḷo capalo mukharo vikiṇṇavāco muṭṭhassati asampajāno asamāhito vibbhantacitto pākatindriyo. "
msgstr "It’s a person who is restless, insolent, fickle, gossipy, loose-tongued, unmindful, lacking situational awareness and immersion, with straying mind and undisciplined faculties. "

msgctxt "an3.115:1.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, puggalo suppameyyo. "
msgstr "This is called ‘a person easy to measure’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.115:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo duppameyyo? "
msgstr "And who is the person hard to measure? "

msgctxt "an3.115:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo anuddhato hoti anunnaḷo acapalo amukharo avikiṇṇavāco upaṭṭhitassati sampajāno samāhito ekaggacitto saṃvutindriyo. "
msgstr "It’s a person who is not restless, insolent, fickle, gossipy, or loose-tongued. They have established mindfulness, situational awareness and immersion, with unified mind and restrained faculties. "

msgctxt "an3.115:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, puggalo duppameyyo. "
msgstr "This is called ‘a person hard to measure’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.115:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo appameyyo? "
msgstr "And who is the immeasurable person? "

msgctxt "an3.115:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu arahaṃ hoti khīṇāsavo. "
msgstr "It’s a mendicant who is perfected, and has ended defilements. "

msgctxt "an3.115:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, puggalo appameyyo. "
msgstr "This is called ‘an immeasurable person’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.115:3.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.115:3.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

